data.description: What a great opportunity to taking in the fabulous panoramic views of the Sierra Mountains & maintain complete privacy from any neighbors. From first entering your privacy gate w/an asphalt circular driveway that offers ample parking, to the front manicured yard w/mature landscaping to the mountain views! Once stepping inside of the home, there are so many pluses here! Very comfortable living w/a lovely formal entry leading to the living & dining rooms. The living room offers a beam ceiling w/ceiling fan, fantastic view windows, wood stove insert & beautiful matching glass hutches that adjoin the dining room. You have so much room in the kitchen w/lots of tiled counter space & a breakfast bar, dbl. ovens, a built-in cooktop that the whole family can cook together! Huge laundry room w/pantry & great utility sink w/tiled counter & lots of storage cabinets too. Master BD is extremely spacious & has breathtaking views from the private sliding glass doors to the patio & a drop dead gorgeous gigantic walk-in closet w/a sit down vanity! There are oversized closets at every turn, whether in the hall, guest BA, the master BA & more, you will have no problem finding room for your wardrobe or having enough storage space. Another room w/built-in shelves that could be an office, den, craft room or whatever you would like to turn this into. The covered back patio & a special deck, lovely landscaping, great shop w/electric, 2 car attached garage, gated & fenced on 3.54+/- stunning acres!
